      "name": "Hemolysis bench comparison — CFX 15 pre-release validation run",
      "description": "ValidationResult produced by comparing CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (nIH) against five FDA bench experimental conditions. Simulation was executed under ModelConfiguration ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2, which was the release candidate immediately preceding the production build. The validation team noted that the rc2 and release builds are 'effectively the same build' — only a documentation patch and a solver log-format change were merged between rc2 and the released version — and therefore elected not to re-execute the full Monte Carlo sweep under the released binary. Achieved agreement within ±12% nIH across all five operating points.",
